=== db-router-decision.md ===
```yaml
feature: "Show SGM time-in-stage breach alongside their coaching usage heatmap"
databases:
  bigquery:
    in_scope: true
    reason: "SGM time-in-stage is opportunity stage progression data in vw_funnel_master / vw_funnel_audit on BigQuery."
  neon_savvy_dashboard:
    in_scope: false
    reason: "No Dashboard-owned Prisma tables (Goal/Forecast/etc.) are read or written for this view."
  neon_sales_coaching:
    in_scope: true
    reason: "Coaching usage heatmap is computed from evaluations + call_notes in sales_coaching, read by Dashboard via direct pg."
preread_paths:
  bigquery:
    - .claude/bq-views.md
    - .claude/bq-field-dictionary.md
    - .claude/bq-patterns.md
    - .claude/bq-activity-layer.md
    - .claude/bq-salesforce-mapping.md
  neon_sales_coaching:
    - .claude/neon-sales-coaching.md
mcp_tools:
  bigquery:
    - schema-context.describe_view
    - schema-context.get_rule
    - schema-context.get_metric
    - schema-context.resolve_term
    - schema-context.lint_query
  neon_sales_coaching:
    - mcp__Neon__describe_table_schema
```

